模板
1、变量
模板:
* {{name}}
* {{age}}
* {{company}}  //转义html
* {{{company}}}  //不转义html
* {{&company}}  //不转义html

视图对象:
{
  "name": "Chris",
  "company": "<b>GitHub</b>"
}

输出:
* Chris
*
* &lt;b&gt;GitHub&lt;/b&gt;
* <b>GitHub</b>
* <b>GitHub</b>

可以使用属性访问格式
模板:
* {{name.first}} {{name.last}}
* {{age}}

视图对象:
{
  "name": {
    "first": "Michael",
    "last": "Jackson"
  },
  "age": "RIP"
}

输出:
* Michael Jackson
* RIP

2、小节
1）、false值（undefined、null、''）或空列表——不展现
模板:
Shown.
{{#nothin}}
Never shown!
{{/nothin}}

视图数据:
{
  "person": true
}

输出:
Shown.

2）、非空列表
模板:
{{#stooges}}
<b>{{name}}</b>
{{/stooges}}

视图:
{
  "stooges": [
    { "name": "Moe" },
    { "name": "Larry" },
    { "name": "Curly" }
  ]
}

输出:
<b>Moe</b>
<b>Larry</b>
<b>Curly</b>

注意：当视图是一个字符串数组时，“.”用于指定当前的选项
模板:
{{#musketeers}}
* {{.}}
{{/musketeers}}

视图数据:
{
  "musketeers": ["Athos", "Aramis", "Porthos", "D'Artagnan"]
}

输出:
* Athos
* Aramis
* Porthos
* D'Artagnan

注意：当变量是一个函数，它将在当前对象的上下文中调用
模板:
{{#beatles}}
* {{name}}
{{/beatles}}

视图:
{
  "beatles": [
    { "firstName": "John", "lastName": "Lennon" },
    { "firstName": "Paul", "lastName": "McCartney" },
    { "firstName": "George", "lastName": "Harrison" },
    { "firstName": "Ringo", "lastName": "Starr" }
  ],
  "name": function () {
    return this.firstName + " " + this.lastName;
  }
}

输出:
* John Lennon
* Paul McCartney
* George Harrison
* Ringo Starr

3）、函数：If the value of a section key is a function, it is called with the section's literal block of text, un-rendered, as its first argument. The second argument is a special rendering function that uses the current view as its view argument. It is called in the context of the current view object.
模板:
{{#bold}}Hi {{name}}.{{/bold}}

视图:
{
  "name": "Tater",
  "bold": function () {
    return function (text, render) {
      return "<b>" + render(text) + "</b>";
    }
  }
}

输出:
<b>Hi Tater.</b>

4）、反向小节
An inverted section opens with {{^section}} instead of {{#section}}. The block of an inverted section is rendered only if the value of that section's tag is null, undefined, false, or an empty list.

模板:
{{#repos}}<b>{{name}}</b>{{/repos}}
{{^repos}}No repos :({{/repos}}

视图:
{
  "repos": []
}

输出:
No repos :(

3、注释
Comments begin with a bang and are ignored. The following template:

<h1>Today{{! ignore me }}.</h1>
Will render as follows:

<h1>Today.</h1>
Comments may contain newlines.

